<p><b>Is communication an academic skill?</b> Communication skills are important for success in all areas of life, but they are especially important in academics. Students who communicate effectively with their teachers, classmates, and other stakeholders are likelier to succeed in school.</p>
<p><b>Is listening is a skill?</b> Listening is one of the essential soft skills. It indicates a person's ability to receive and interpret information in the communication process. Without active listening skills, you won't be able to receive and interpret the message.</p>